I don't know why but this make me sooooooo saddddddd
1st: The beginning of 2020, with no music from WDW, how can I live through that, and the beginning of this year, it's when I need them the most! like OMG! Someone save meeeeeee!
2nd: I'm an international fan! How the hell can I text them! Like I need them sooooooo muchhhhhhhhhhhhh in this moment! And they said 'text us if you need us' ,but HOW!
3rd: I heard about the 1D things, and I'm scared right now! I LITERALLY don't want them to break the band! They are one of the best thing that happened to my life! They belong together! And I want them to stick as a band until they got old! I know that they're just taking a break but like I STILL FEEL SCARED OK! WELL I'M NOT OK, SO YOU CAN TELL BY THE WAY I WRITE THIS!

Please can someone just comfort me! Or I'm just gonna comfort myself by listening to ALL of their from the start till now, and watching interviews of them!( Well that's literally what I do everyday, tell me if that's what you do too) Their music are soooooooooo damn catchy, I can't stop listening to it, like LITERALLY CAN'T!!! Every time I stop, I just want to continue listen to it soooooooooooo bad, or I will feel bad that I didn't listen to their music and watching their interview, it's so hard to stop listen, to stop watching them

Tell me if you're just the same as me....I felt super lonely without WDW right now! OMG!!!
ONCE A LIMELIGHT!🍋💡
ALWAYS A LIMELIGHT!!🍋💡
LIMELIGHT FOREVER!!!🍋💡

snippet.textDisplay: I have mixed feelings. I am so happy for them to take a break because I  am sure being in a band is super stressful. I am soooo happy I can text them now because I have always dreamed of contacting them. But I am going to miss the monthly songs and the posts on Instagram. I am really going to miss the boys in general. But I am sure they are going to come back with the best music possible. I am sure that they will come back and they will be much happier from getting a chance away from the stress. I am sure the world tour was so stressful and I am sure a break will be good. Besides they have time to resolve any band tension if there is any. I love why don’t we so much and as much as I hate hate HATE not being able to have a monthly song and posts on Instagram, they are only going to come back stronger. And I will be here waiting for there new songs and waiting for my tickets to their next tour. Besides jachary shipper or not we all know jack needs time with lav and his family. Same with the rest of the boys they have people in their live that they need more time with. So we can’t hate on the boys for leaving. I can’t even be upset I am just so ready for the boys to come out with the most AMAZING songs I am going to listen to on repeat for hours. So here’s to 2020 the boys best music year yet. 🥂It’ll be worth the wait but the boys will come through. 🖤
